{"tid":2289562,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女人幾時先會面對男友/老公真係會愛上第個女人","createTime":"2020-11-17T10:37:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T09:47:34.000Z","uid":373544,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"723d258d4c59aef7a7790b5c8212163a1b9c4b57","tid":2289562,"uid":373544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T10:37:26.000Z","msg":"成日聽啲女人話男人偷食唔會動真情<br />\n只係因為鳩痕貪玩 <br />\n係啊 係鳩痕貪玩嘅 但唔代表佢對嗰啲女人會唔動情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人板：洗米華<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Wx2C8E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Wx2C8E.jpg&h=b8a612df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當年佢喺記者面前自己拖實咗二奶mandy lieu<br />\n平時又山長水遠都飛英國飛泰國揾Mandy<br />\n用喺mandy身上嘅錢分分鐘多過用喺大婆身上嘅<br />\n男人唔想離婚係因為唔想俾你分身家 就唔係因為佢有幾愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔想分手就只係因為唔想浪費放過喺你身上嘅錢同時間<br />\n請各位有伴侶/已婚女士好好面對<br />\n唔好再喺啲飯局話男人點會真係愛第三者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />在場男士好尷尬又要逼住附和下你<br />\n男人求你原諒佢嗰時講話當外面條女係水泡乜乜柒柒<br />\n真定假自己心照啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要拎出嚟同人講你另一半咁講 以為人哋咁就會覺得你另一半真係好愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n望到你啲水桶腰同又粗又O形嘅腳 加埋平時為人巴渣計較啲閪格 都知你條仔愛極你有限啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eecb6956901df00b7ca0e6853aa0425b79e87c9","tid":2289562,"uid":15758,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T10:41:06.000Z","msg":"起左樓豬底 一係死毒撚一係帶過綠帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑死"},{"pid":"ad4a2f554c1a667015fb2f7ffc23274eedf9c22b","tid":2289562,"uid":91767,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"723d258d4c59aef7a7790b5c8212163a1